snippet.title: Gorilla gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Gorilla (aka qbasic gorillas), Dos PC game produced by Microsoft in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/gorilla/5790/
Playing through a few games of this simple but addictive strategy game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
